						               													<description>Totem Hoarder is a fast-paced strategy card duel.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Two players assume the roles of rival archeologists and artifact collectors, racing to get a hold of magical Totems. By getting 1 card and playing 1 card each turn, both players assembles teams of creatures on the table in front of them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On a player's turn, they normally draw 1 card from the common pile and play 1 card by putting it into their team - their respective side of the battlefield.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Most of the cards in the draw pile are creatures that can be played to perform various actions. But some cards are Totems and follow a slightly different set of rules: If a played Totem in interrupted with a Spooky Skelly, that Totem immediately switches teams! Totems are also &amp;quot;indestructible&amp;quot; - if you attack an opponent's Totem, move it into your own team instead of discarding it.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The first player to have three Totems (and no Spooky Skellies) in their team wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
